      public Categorized<?> containerCategorized()
      Returns the set of categories (Category) associated to this container. If this container has variables and parameters, they are specified by these categories.

      the object holding all the category information

    • parameters

      public TwData parameters()
      Returns the parameter set associated to this container. It is specified by the categories associated to the container, accessible through the categoryInfo() method.

      the parameter set - may be null
